name: Spaceport Docking Bay
LocationDStext: Your docking bay transit from here requires 2 Force. Your fighters deploy -1 (or -2 if freighter) here. May not deploy to Bespin, Dagobah, Endor, Hoth or Yavin 4.
LocationLStext: Your docking bay transit from here requires 3 Force. Your pilots deploy +1 here. May not deploy to Bespin, Dagobah, Endor, Hoth or Yavin 4.
